    "body": "Starship sets the nushell option `render_right_prompt_on_last_line = true` for this reason. Your config file is truncated in your issue, but it is possible that your config causes this setting to be lost, thus please try rearranging your nu config such that this does not happen or try adding the setting to your main config.",
